snippet.title: Naima's Melody - Title Screen
snippet.description:
Naima's Melody is an upcoming 2D action adventure game inspired by classics such as The Legend of Zelda series. The game is being developed in RPG Maker MV.

For more information please follow us on our development twitter:
twitter.com/JumpGameStudio
